---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Container from '~/components/layout/Container.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — Emberstone Database">
  <Container size="md" class="mt-12 prose-ash">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl tracking-tight text-ash-50">About this database</h1>
    <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-ash-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Emberstone Database is the canonical reference for our Classic 1.12.1 realm.
        Every quest, item, NPC, and spell shown here is derived from the live
        world database the worldserver actually reads on startup — so if the
        site disagrees with the game, it's the site that's stale, not the
        server.
      </p>
      <p>
        Data is dumped from MariaDB to JSON on every fork release (image push to
        <code class="font-mono text-ember-300">ghcr.io/xunholy/cmangos-classic</code>)
        and Astro statically renders every detail page. Stock entries get tooltips
        from <a href="https://www.wowhead.com/classic" class="text-ember-300">Wowhead Classic</a>
        on hover; everything Emberstone-specific is rendered natively with source
        links into <a href="https://github.com/xunholy/cmangos-classic" class="text-ember-300">xunholy/cmangos-classic</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        The site is intentionally narrow in scope: Classic 1.12.1 only, fork-aware,
        no AH listings or live auction tools. For account registration and
        the realm portal, head over to
        <a href="https://emberstone.owncloud.ai" class="text-ember-300">emberstone.owncloud.ai</a>.
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-ash-50 mt-10">Built with</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li><a href="https://astro.build" class="text-ember-300">Astro</a> + React islands</li>
        <li><a href="https://tailwindcss.com" class="text-ember-300">Tailwind CSS</a> with a bespoke ember palette</li>
        <li><a href="https://cmdk.paco.me" class="text-ember-300">cmdk</a> for the search palette</li>
        <li>MariaDB 11 + mysql2 for the build-time data dump</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-ash-500 text-sm pt-4 border-t border-ash-800 mt-8">
        World of Warcraft is a trademark of Blizzard Entertainment. This project
        exists for education and private-server experimentation; no commercial use.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</BaseLayout>
